Package com.opengamma.strata.collect.tuple

Class ObjIntPair<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.collect.tuple.ObjIntPair<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the type of the object
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tuple, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ObjIntPair<A>>, org.joda.beans.Bean, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean
    public final class ObjIntPair<A>
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean, Tuple, java.lang.Comparable<ObjIntPair<A>>, java.io.Serializable
    An immutable pair consisting of an Object and an int.

    This class is similar to Pair but includes a primitive element.

    This class is immutable and thread-safe.
